Tofu Chocolate Mousse
  -Martha Stewart

3/4 c chocolate chips
12 oz room temp silken tofu (1 container)
1/2 c warmed milk
1 oz finely chopped chocolate (or 2 tbsp chocolate chips) for garnish

Microwave chocolate chips in 30s increments, stirring each time, until melted. In a food processor, puree melted chocolate with tofu and warmed milk until smooth. Force mixture through a sieve into a medium bowl, pressing with a spoon. Scoop into 4 serving dishes and refrigerate until chilled, ~30 min. Garnish with the finely chopped chocolate or chocolate chips if desired.
